.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-TEST" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.2.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-test \- Smoke\-test a compose spec end to end
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose test [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Validate, prepare, render, launch, and evaluate a finite compose smoke test. Choose \-\-local for the local Pyxis/Enroot supervisor or \-\-submit for a short Slurm submission.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read; if omitted, use the active context compose file or fall back to compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--enroot\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the enroot executable. Default: enroot.
.TP
\fB--apptainer\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the apptainer executable. Default: apptainer.
.TP
\fB--singularity\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the singularity executable. Default: singularity.
.TP
\fB--huggingface\-cli\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the huggingface\-cli used by hf:// stage_in inside the job (default: huggingface\-cli). Default: huggingface\-cli.
.TP
\fB--keep\-failed\-prep\fR
Keep failed preparation state on disk for later inspection.
.TP
\fB--skip\-prepare\fR
Skip image import and prepare reuse checks.
.TP
\fB--force\-rebuild\fR
Refresh imported and prepared artifacts before running.
.TP
\fB--no\-preflight\fR
Skip the preflight phase before running.
.TP
\fB--local\fR
Run the smoke test through the local Pyxis/Enroot supervisor.
.TP
\fB--submit\fR
Submit the smoke test to Slurm.
.TP
\fB--time\fR \fITIME\fR
Walltime override for \-\-submit smoke tests. Default: 00:01:00.
.TP
\fB--timeout\fR \fIDURATION\fR
Maximum time to wait for the smoke test to reach a terminal result. Default: 180s.
.TP
\fB--script\-out\fR \fIOUTPUT\fR
Write the rendered launcher script to this path.
.TP
\fB--sbatch\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sbatch executable. Default: sbatch.
.TP
\fB--srun\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the srun executable. Default: srun.
.TP
\fB--squeue\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the squeue executable. Default: squeue.
.TP
\fB--sacct\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sacct executable. Default: sacct.
.TP
\fB--scancel\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the scancel executable. Default: scancel.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose test \-\-local \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose test \-\-submit \-\-time 00:01:00 \-f compose.yaml
hpc\-compose test \-\-submit \-\-timeout 180s \-\-format json \-f compose.yaml
.fi
